%20ready%20for%20the%20AI%20chip%20company%20he%20had%20long%20considered%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20then%2C%20Huang%20had%20worked%20on%20MediaTek's%20GPUs%2C%20Apple's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFace%20ID%20technology%2C%20and%20at%20an%20Amazon%20AI%20chip%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20ChatGPT%20burst%20onto%20the%20scene%20in%20late%202022%2C%20Huang%20became%20convinced%20the%20industry%20had%20reached%20a%20turning%20point.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20the%20market%20had%20arrived%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20at%2055%2C%20Huang%20decided%20to%20start%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20he%20founded%20Tranxform%20AI%2C%20a%20Taiwan-based%20AI%20chip%20startup%20developing%20power-efficient%20processors%20designed%20to%20run%20AI%20models%20outside%20large%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20now%20employs%20about%2040%20people%20and%20is%20preparing%20its%20first%20chip%2C%20which%20Huang%20expects%20to%20be%20ready%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20is%20among%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20entrepreneurs%20chasing%20opportunities%20created%20by%20the%20AI%20boom.%20Unlike%20many%20founders%20building%20companies%20around%20large%20language%20models%2C%20however%2C%20he%20spent%20decades%20designing%20chips%20before%20launching%20his%20own%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Huang%20never%20viewed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturning-40-midlife-crisis-career-rebrand-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eage%20as%20a%20disadvantage.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-billionaire-founder-morris-chang-lessons-business-leadership-advice-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMorris%20Chang%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20TSMC%20in%20his%2050s%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsm-stock-price-valuation-ai-demand-nvda-tech-earnings-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETaiwan%20Semiconductor%20Manufacturing%20Company%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20founded%20the%20world's%20largest%20contract%20chipmaker%20at%2055.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Huang%20believes%20age%20may%20be%20on%20his%20side%2C%20arguing%20that%20hardware%20startups%20often%20favor%20experience%20in%20ways%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-founders-raising-millions-for-their-ai-startups-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esoftware%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E%20do%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESemiconductor%20design%20is%20a%20long%20game%2C%20he%20said.%20Building%20a%20system-on-a-chip%20%E2%80%94%20the%20integrated%20processor%20that%20powers%20devices%20ranging%20from%20smartphones%20to%20AI%20systems%20%E2%80%94%20requires%20balancing%20countless%20tradeoffs%20across%20hardware%20and%20software%2C%20a%20skill%20that%20can%20take%20decades%20to%20develop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20build%20a%20good%20SoC%2C%20you%20need%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%20%26quot%3BOtherwise%2C%20you%20would%20not%20know%20how%20to%20balance%20different%20operations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang's%20startup%20adventure%20was%20not%20an%20obvious%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20founding%20Tranxform%2C%20he%20had%20a%20stable%20career%20and%20a%20comfortable%20income%20in%20the%20US.%20Building%20the%20company%20meant%20taking%20a%20significant%20risk%20and%20spending%20most%20of%20his%20time%20in%20Taiwan%2C%20a%20decision%20his%20family%20initially%20struggled%20to%20accept.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Tranxform%20grew%20and%20reached%20key%20milestones%2C%20his%20family's%20attitude%20changed.%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20they%20are%20proud%20of%20what%20we%20have%20accomplished%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20timing%20also%20helped.%20Huang's%20two%20sons%20were%20adults%20when%20he%20founded%20the%20company.%20One%20works%20in%20the%20technology%20industry%2C%20while%20the%20other%20recently%20graduated%20from%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20them%20become%20independent%20has%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20dedicate%20the%20time%20and%20energy%20needed%20to%20build%20Tranxform%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehe%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebelieved%20the%20risk%20was%20worth%20taking%20because%20demand%20for%20specialized%20AI%20hardware%20would%20continue%20growing%20as%20companies%20looked%20for%20faster%20and%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-centers-us-chips-electricity-power-crunch-shortage-goldman-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eenergy-efficient%20ways%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20run%20increasingly%20complex%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang's%20optimism%20comes%20as%20investors%20pour%20fresh%20capital%20into%20AI%20hardware.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVenture%20funding%20for%20AI%20and%20machine-learning%20chip%20startups%20rose%20over%2070%25%20to%20%2416.2%20billion%20in%202025%20from%20the%20year%20before%2C%20according%20to%20PitchBook.%20However%2C%20the%20number%20of%20deals%20fell%20to%20232%20from%20266%20in%20the%20same%20period%20as%20investors%20increasingly%20wrote%20bigger%20checks%20to%20a%20smaller%20cohort%20of%20potential%20breakout%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20funding%20stood%20at%20%249.9%20billion%20as%20of%20June%2022%2C%20with%20deal%20counts%20at%2087%2C%20per%20PitchBook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F6MOxj%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Column%20Chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F6MOxj%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc9f6926-40cb-46e0-b614-8cf6d6b84fc8%5C%22%3EReturning%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20