nd-tv-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eparkour%20class%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20in%20their%2050s%2C%2060s%2C%20and%2070s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c7d6804-6cbe-40b4-ad9e-65ead251b1af%5C%22%3EFinding%20his%20footing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20morning%20session%20was%20one%20of%20seven%20classes%20that%20Tan%20Shie%20Boon%2C%20a%20parkour%20coach%20and%20founder%20of%20Movement.sg%2C%20teaches%20each%20week%20across%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParkour%20is%20often%20associated%20with%20young%20athletes%20performing%20daring%20jumps%20and%20flips%20as%20they%20weave%20through%20urban%20landscapes.%20But%20over%20the%20past%20several%20years%2C%20Tan%20has%20carved%20out%20a%20niche%20teaching%20parkour%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthy-aging-singapore-longevity-fitness-wellness-team-strong-silvers-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eolder%20adults%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20flashy%20stunts%2C%20Tan%20wants%20his%20students%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20navigate%20obstacles%2C%20recover%20their%20balance%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20get%20up%20safely%20if%20they%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20skill%20set%20he%20considers%20essential%2C%20given%20that%20falls%20are%20the%20leading%20cause%20of%20injury%20among%20adults%20ages%2065%20and%20older%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Ffalls%2Fdata-research%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20CDC%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20problem%20that%20is%20very%20prevalent%2C%26quot%3B%20Tan%2C%2034%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BTo%20me%2C%20it's%20almost%20ridiculous%20that%20people%20overlook%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223470%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20vaulting%20over%20a%20railing.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b9b5e3d84808d83754dfb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222602%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStudents%20spend%20much%20of%20the%20class%20traversing%20their%20surroundings%20%E2%80%94%20hopping%20across%20ledges%2C%20vaulting%20over%20railings%2C%20and%20negotiating%20obstacles%20along%20the%20way.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETan's%20path%20to%20this%20career%20was%20long%20and%20winding.%20As%20a%20student%2C%20he%20thought%20he'd%20pursue%20computer%20science%2C%20but%20the%20plan%20never%20felt%20quite%20right.%20At%20his%20brother's%20suggestion%2C%20Tan%20enrolled%20at%20a%20local%20arts%20school%20to%20study%20dance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20there%20that%20his%20interest%20in%20parkour%20began%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etake%20root.%20A%20workshop%20led%20by%20visiting%20practitioners%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrench-parkour-group-uses-skills-to-turn-off-street-lights-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efrom%20France%3C%2Fa%3E%20gave%20him%20his%20first%20real%20exposure%20to%20the%20discipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomething%20about%20how%20they%20carry%20themselves%20kind%20of%20aligned%20with%20how%20I%20wanted%20to%20live%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Tan%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20very%20free-spirited%2C%20and%20they%20are%20very%20dedicated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20he%20felt%20constrained%20by%20both%20society%20and%20his%20dance%20training%2C%20parkour%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20felt%20powerful%20and%20liberating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20parkour%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20could%20be%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20Tan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETan%20left%20the%20arts%20school%20and%20worked%20odd%20jobs%20to%20pay%20for%20his%20training%20at%20the%20now-defunct%20ADD%20Academy%20Singapore%2C%20a%20parkour%20school%20founded%20by%20that%20same%20French%20group.%20He%20became%20an%20instructor%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224427%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20watching%20as%20another%20older%20man%20does%20a%20jump%20across%20two%20playground%20structures.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a45eee1ec11c5f7e7fa7776%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223635%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20Tan%2C%20parkour%20represented%20a%20kind%20of%20freedom%20he%20hadn't%20found%20elsewhere.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2249ab1db0-c767-4733-9b2d-3872156c5421%5C%22%3EMaking%20the%20leap%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETan's%20focus%20on%20teaching%20older%20adults%2C%20however%2C%20came%20about%20by%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20he%20met%20a%20then-64-year-old%20woman%20at%20a%20food%20court%20while%20waiting%20in%20line%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%20She%20asked%20him%20what%20he%20did%20for%20a%20living%2C%20and%20became%20intrigued%20when%20he%20said%20he%20was%20a%20parkour%20coach.%20She%20had%20never%20heard%20of%20the%20discipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20showed%20her%20videos%2C%20and%20she%20asked%20me%20if%20this%20could%20help%20her%20with%20her%20balance.%20I%20said%2C%20absolutely%2C%20because%20we%20practice%20balancing%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20Tan%20said.%20The%20pair%20met%20the%20following%20day%20and%20began%20training%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20him%20she%20couldn't%20walk%20without%20a%20trolley%20cart%20for%20stability%2C%20fearing%20she%20would%20otherwise%20fall.%20After%20several%20months%20of%20training%2C%20Tan%20said%2C%20she%20became%20increasingly%20confident%20moving%20around%20unaided.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222525%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20doing%20a%20single-leg%20squat%2C%20unassisted.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a46112bec11c5f7e7fa7793%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223367%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20addition%20to%20parkour%20drills%2C%20students%20also%20do%20bodyweight%20exercises%2C%20such%20as%20single-leg%20squats.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20local%20news%20outlet%20picked%20up%20on%20her%20story%2C%20and%20the%20media%20attention%20brought%20a%20wave%20of%20inquiries%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnot-retiring-work-healthy-aging-walking-splits-community-diet-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretirees%20across%20Singapore%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20when%20I%20realized%20that%2C%20hey%2C%20this%20could%20be%20a%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Tan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETan%20isn't%20the%20only%20coach%20adapting%20parkour%20for%20older%20adults.%20Similar%20programs%20have%20emerged%20in%20the%20US%2C%20including%20PK%20Move's%20PK%20Silver%20program%20in%20Northern%20Virginia%20and%20Parkour%20Generations%20Boston.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20people%20who%20reached%20out%20back%20then%20are%20still%20training%20with%20Tan%20today.%20Among%20them%20is%20Sarah%20Wang%2C%2061%2C%20a%20retired%20preschool%20teacher.%20Intrigued%20by%20the%20news%20coverage%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try%20in%202018%20and%20has%20been%20attending%20Tan's%20classes%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20said%20she%20enjoys%20that%20no%20two%20sessions%20are%20exactly%20alike.%20Each%20location%20offers%20a%20different%20environment%20to%20navigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20test%20yourself%20and%20challenge%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20said.%20Outside%20of%20Tan's%20classes%2C%20walking%20is%20her%20primary%20form%20of%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20six%20months%20after%20Wang%20signed%20up%2C%20her%20friend%20Ling%20Ying%20Ying%20followed%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELing%2C%20who%20attends%20classes%20twice%20a%20week%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20has%20noticed%20improvements%20in%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-improved-mobility-flexibility-reformer-pilates-classes-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estrength%20and%20mobility%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223763%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20guiding%20a%20woman%20to%20vault%20over%20a%20railing.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a45eee12680585ce91a3796%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222822%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20of%20his%20students%20have%20been%20attending%20Tan's%20parkour%20sessions%20since%202018.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20first%20started%20the%20class%2C%20I%20actually%20had%20problems%20going%20down%20the%20stairs.%20I%20had%20to%20go%20down%20sideways%20because%20walking%20down%20normally%20caused%20pain%20in%20my%20knees%2C%26quot%3B%20Ling%2C%2066%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20I%20started%20parkour%2C%20my%20knees%20became%20stronger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20growing%20scientific%20interest%20in%20adapting%20parkour%20principles%20for%20older%20adults%2C%20Shawn%20Soh%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20Singapore%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenefits%20include%20%26quot%3Bimprovements%20in%20agility%2C%20lower-limb%20strength%2C%20dynamic%20balance%2C%20postural%20control%2C%20coordination%2C%20and%20environmental%20awareness%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Soh%2C%20who%20is%20trained%20in%20physiotherapy%20and%20specializes%20in%20ortho-geriatric%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20also%20improve%20what%20researchers%20call%20falls%20efficacy%20%E2%80%94%20a%20person's%20confidence%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fbalance-exercises-for-seniors%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emaintaining%20balance%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20recovering%20from%20a%20stumble%2C%20and%20getting%20up%20safely%20after%20a%20fall%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Soh%20cautioned%20that%20the%20training%20carries%20risks.%20Older%20adults%2C%20particularly%20those%20with%20osteoporosis%20or%20low%20bone%20density%2C%20may%20be%20more%20susceptible%20to%20fractures.%20He%20added%20that%20sprains%2C%20strains%2C%20bruising%2C%20and%20falls%20are%20all%20possible%2C%20and%20that%20higher-intensity%20movements%20can%20place%20greater%20demands%20on%20the%20heart%20and%20cardiovascular%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOlder%20adults%20should%20understand%20their%20own%20health%20status%2C%20medical%20conditions%2C%20and%20physical%20capabilities%20before%20starting%20any%20new%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20Soh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETan%20said%20his%20classes%20are%20designed%20with%20those%20differences%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221787%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20attempting%20to%20jump%20across%20a%20ledge.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4611b7ec11c5f7e7fa7795%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222383%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMost%20classes%20draw%20between%20four%20and%2012%20participants%2C%20although%20he%20says%20he%20has%20about%2030%20students%20in%20total.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20teaching%20parkour%20to%20seniors%20may%20sound%20risky%2C%20Tan%20said%20he%20guides%20participants%20through%20movements%20at%20their%20own%20pace.%20Exercises%20can%20be%20modified%20for%20those%20who%20are%20less%20confident%20or%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folder-american-workers-health-issues-challenges-disabilities-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emobility%20limitations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a14461d4-71c4-4837-9c4a-c5a0d497b4d6%5C%22%3EGoing%20the%20distance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETan%20now%20runs%20the%20business%20by%20himself.%20Each%2090-minute%20class%20costs%2035%20Singapore%20dollars%2C%20or%20about%20%2426%2C%20and%20most%20classes%20draw%20between%20four%20and%2012%20participants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20is%20enough%20to%20sustain%20him%2C%20though%20he%20said%20he%20earns%20less%20than%20when%20he%20previously%20ran%20another%20parkour%20coaching%20business%20with%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20live%20a%20lifestyle%20where%20I%20spend%20a%20lot%2C%20so%20it's%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20Tan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BManaging%20a%20team%20is%20very%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20much%20prefer%20my%20life%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETan%20hopes%20that%2C%20one%20day%2C%20some%20of%20his%20longtime%20students%20will%20become%20coaches%20themselves.%20For%20now%2C%20though%2C%20he%20says%20the%20lessons%20often%20flow%20both%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20grow%20old%2C%20I%20want%20to%20be%20like%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20prove%20to%20me%20that%20they%20have%20the%20never-say-die%20spirit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparkour-seniors-older-adults-healthy-aging-balance-training-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783293241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a44ae1aa25092c74cca1d5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparkour-seniors-older-adults-healthy-aging-balance-training-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parkour%20classes%20for%20older%20adults%20focus%20on%20balance%2C%20strength%2C%20and%20recovering%20safely%20from%20falls.%20See%20how%20these%20seniors%20are%20redefining%20healthy%20aging.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40businessinsider.com%20(Amanda%20Goh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22FMCG%20Q1%20demand%20stable%3B%20companies%20flag%20El%20Nino%20risk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783292777000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132204773%2Cimgsize-1451809.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimes