ow%2F132202867.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F132202867.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Minions%20have%20narrowly%20edged%20out%20'Toy%20Story%205'%20for%20the%20July%20Fourth%20weekend%20box%20office%20crown%2C%20with%20'Minions%20%26amp%3B%20Monsters'%20raking%20in%20USD%20160%20million%20worldwide.%20'Toy%20Story%205'%20followed%20with%20USD%2031%20million.%20Meanwhile%2C%20historical%20drama%20'Young%20Washington'%20captured%20third%20place%2C%20appealing%20to%20patriotic%20audiences.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Just%2028%25%20NGOs%2C%20associations%20ever%20registered%20under%20FCRA%20currently%20active%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783287043000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132202941%2Cimgsize-1135942.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fjust-28-ngos-associations-ever-registered-under-fcra-currently-active%2Farticleshow%2F132202940.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20significant%20majority%20of%20NGOs%20registered%20under%20the%20Foreign%20Contribution%20(Regulation)%20Act%2C%202010%2C%20are%20no%20longer%20active%2C%20with%20over%2072%25%20having%20their%20licenses%20cancelled%20or%20expired.%20Since%202012%2C%20out%20of%2052%2C159%20granted%20licenses%2C%20only%2014%2C455%20currently%20hold%20active%20status%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20receive%20foreign%20funding.%20This%20tightening%20of%20regulations%20aims%20to%20enhance%20accountability%20and%20transparency%20among%20these%20organizations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22BHARTI%20JAIN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%2075-year-old%20retiree%20in%20Newark.%20My%20partner%20and%20I%20spend%20%24150%20a%20week%20on%20groceries%20and%20save%20money%20by%20skipping%20meat.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22John%20Goldstein%20with%20his%20home%20garden.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a46bca2e3bd3a50082bfc81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn%20Goldstein%20grows%20tomatoes%20and%20herbs%20to%20have%20fresh%20ingredients%20to%20cook%20with.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Goldstein%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJohn%20Goldstein%2C%20a%2075-year-old%20retiree%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20spends%20about%20%24150%20a%20week%20on%20food%20for%20him%20and%20his%20partner.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESkipping%20meat%20and%20avoiding%20restaurants%20helps%20him%20balance%20his%20budget%20against%20rising%20healthcare%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20says%20frugality%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20unenjoyable%20for%20those%20willing%20to%20learn%20new%20ways%20to%20cook%20at%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20John%20Goldstein%2C%20a%2075-year-old%20retiree%20in%20Newark%2C%20New%20Jersey.%20The%20interview%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20retired%20people%20in%20our%20country%2C%20I%20live%20on%20a%20fixed%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20live%20with%20my%20partner%2C%20who%20is%20also%20retired%20and%20on%20a%20fixed%20income%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20a%20choice%20to%20think%20a%20lot%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-are-rising-prices-affecting-your-food-bills-share-receipts-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20cost%20of%20food%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20not%20just%20the%20cost%20of%20food.%20The%20costs%20of%20housing%20and%20healthcare%20have%20had%20a%20huge%20impact%20on%20us.%20Paying%20the%20Medicare%20premium%20eats%20up%20whatever%20cost-of-living%20adjustment%20Social%20Security%20provides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20I'm%20very%20different%20in%20that%20respect%20from%20lots%20of%20retired%20people%20on%20a%20fixed%20income%20when%20prices%20are%20going%20up.%20People's%20incomes%20are%20not%20anywhere%20close%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcpi-inflation-may-consumer-price-index-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ekeeping%20up%20with%20inflation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2276e9b0d3-f31c-4f8d-9911-e0840c924fc8%5C%22%3EFood%20costs%20are%20a%20big%20part%20of%20what%20we%20can%20control%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20can't%20control%20the%20cost%20of%20healthcare%2C%20but%20with%20food%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20it%20is%20discretionary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20friends%20who%20like%20hanging%20out%20at%20the%20bar%2C%20and%20that%20ends%20up%20costing%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20We%20don't%20do%20that%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20used%20to%20eat%20at%20restaurants%20four%20or%20five%20times%20a%20month.%20Now%20it's%20maybe%20four%20or%20five%20times%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20partner%20was%20pescatarian%20when%20we%20met%2014%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20giving%20up%20meat%20has%20saved%20us%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20If%20we%20were%20still%20eating%20meat%2C%20we%20probably%20would%20have%20stopped%20because%20the%20price%20has%20gone%20up%20so%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20also%20changed%20how%20and%20where%20I%20shop%20for%20groceries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20local%20Portuguese%20markets%2C%20when%20I%20moved%20here%20to%20Newark%2015%20years%20ago%2C%20were%20the%20cheapest%20markets%20around.%20They're%20now%20like%20Whole%20Foods%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrocery-store-ready-to-eat-replacing-restaurants-trends-competition-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprepared%20foods%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20expensive%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20to%20go%20to%20Whole%20Foods%20once%20in%20a%20while%2C%20too%2C%20and%20now%20I%20go%20there%20maybe%20twice%20a%20year%2C%20if%20there's%20something%20I%20can't%20find%20anywhere%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20I%20do%20a%20weekly%20trip%20to%20ShopRite%20and%20am%20careful%20to%20track%20coupons%20and%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20typically%20spend%20about%20%24150%20a%20week%2C%20with%20about%20a%20third%20on%20fresh%20produce%2C%20a%20third%20on%20dairy%20products%20like%20yogurt%20and%20cheese%2C%20and%20a%20third%20on%20pantry%20staples%20like%20nuts%2C%20beans%2C%20olive%20oil%2C%20and%20whatever%20else%20I%20might%20need%20to%20cook%20a%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20day%20I%20was%20shopping%20because%20all%20the%20kids%20and%20grandkids%20were%20visiting%2C%20and%20I%20think%20my%20grocery%20bill%20was%20%24250%2C%20and%20I%20had%20saved%20almost%20%24100%20from%20coupons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20also%20found%20smaller%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-nyc-resident-saves-money-cash-back-apps-hacks-more-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eways%20to%20save%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20used%20to%20eat%20a%20lot%20of%20fresh%20fish%2C%20but%20that's%20gotten%20really%20expensive%2C%20so%20I%20end%20up%20buying%20flash-frozen%20filets%20or%20canned%20fish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20started%20eating%20a%20lot%20more%20beans%20for%20protein%20instead%20of%20fish.%20Canned%20beans%20were%20like%20%241%20a%20can%2C%20but%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20dried%20beans%20is%20around%20%240.25%2C%20so%20that's%20a%20significant%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20buy%20packaged%20goods%20like%20cookies%20and%20cereal%2C%20and%20we%20buy%20very%20little%20processed%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20also%20growing%20some%20tomato%20plants%20and%20some%20herbs%20and%20spices.%20Instead%20of%20buying%20a%20bunch%20of%20cilantro%2C%20parsley%2C%20and%20basil%20at%20the%20store%20and%20having%20most%20of%20it%20spoil%20before%20I%20ever%20use%20it%2C%20I%20can%20pick%20what%20I%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20I'm%20saving%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20with%20the%20garden.%20It%20mainly%20gives%20me%20the%20pleasure%20of%20having%20a%20nice%2C%20flavorful%20homegrown%20tomato.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e00d70bc-97bd-4c99-bac7-5a6d9dccc14e%5C%22%3EWe%20don't%20spend%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20we%20still%20eat%20well%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20frugal%2C%20but%20living%20well%20does%20not%20require%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20We%20live%20extremely%20well.%20We%20eat%20great%20meals%20and%20do%20it%20on%20a%20very%20reasonable%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20to%20cook%2C%20which%20is%20an%20important%20piece%20of%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20happy%20place%20for%20me%20is%20when%20I%20can%20cook%20and%20watch%20a%20soccer%20match%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20Life%20doesn't%20get%20much%20better%20than%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20can%20accept%20that%20changes%20%E2%80%94%20in%20what%20you're%20buying%2C%20in%20what%20you're%20cooking%2C%20or%20in%20what%20you're%20eating%20%E2%80%94%20are%20not%20punitive%2C%20but%20that%20they%20are%20choices%20that%20you're%20making%2C%20you%20can%20find%20ways%20to%20make%20those%20choices%20very%20desirable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20also%20well%20aware%20that%20this%20doesn't%20work%20for%20everybody%2C%20but%20getting%20over%20the%20fear%20of%20cooking%20and%20things%20not%20being%20perfect%20in%20the%20kitchen%20is%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20be%20afraid%20that%20you%20might%20burn%20something.%20You%20%3Cem%3Ewill%3C%2Fem%3E%20burn%20some%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20be%20afraid%20that%20sometimes%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20turn%20out%20perfectly%2C%20because%20sometimes%20it%20won't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20you've%20eaten%20the%20same%20things%20for%20many%20years%2C%20don't%20be%20afraid%20to%20try%20something%20new%20and%20look%20around%20for%20inspiration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20do%20have%20a%20meal%20in%20a%20restaurant%20that%20I%20think%20is%20incredible%2C%20I'll%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20do%20that%20at%20home.%20I'll%20figure%20it%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20once%20went%20to%20this%20restaurant%20in%20San%20Francisco%20that%20had%20trout%20stuffed%20with%20spinach%20and%20feta%2C%20and%20it%20was%20delicious.%20Ten%20years%20later%2C%20I%20was%20still%20thinking%20about%20it%2C%20so%20I%20taught%20myself%20how%20to%20debone%20a%20trout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20so%20complicated%2C%20of%20course%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20terribly%20expensive%2C%20and%20it%20tastes%20really%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBreaking%20the%20chains%20of%20the%20food%20that%20you're%20used%20to%20eating%20and%20branching%20out%20can%20be%20exciting%2C%20it%20can%20be%20fulfilling%2C%20and%20it%20can%20also%20help%20you%20think%20through%20how%20to%20do%20that%20in%20an%20economical%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretiree-in-newark-spends-150-a-week-groceries-food-budget-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783286521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a46bca2e3bd3a50082bfc81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretiree-in-newark-spends-150-a-week-groceries-food-budget-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22John%20Goldstein%2C%20a%2075-year-old%20retiree%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20says%20he%20still%20eats%20well%20even%20as%20he%20budgets%20to%20manage%20rising%20health%20costs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dreuter%40businessinsider.com%20(Dominick%20Reuter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Foundation%20laid%20for%20Rs%202%2C500-crore%20defence%20plant%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783285994000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.to