with%20223%2C000%20accounting%20for%20pure%20album%20sales%20thanks%20to%2030%20CD%20variants%20and%20five%20vinyl%20variants.%20This%20marks%20Ateez%E2%80%99s%20ninth%20top%2010%20on%20the%20albums%20chart%20and%20their%20third%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Steven%20J.%20Horowitz%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20the%20organizer%20in%20my%20friend%20group.%20Someone%20has%20to%20be%2C%20or%20we'd%20never%20see%20each%20other.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20meeting%20for%20coffee%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3aa09a40d09c7636327c7e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20is%20the%20one%20organizing%20friends'%20hangouts.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI've%20spent%20years%20organizing%20gatherings%20for%20my%20female%20friends.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFriendship%20requires%20effort%2C%20especially%20as%20adults%20get%20busier.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBeing%20the%20organizer%20is%20less%20glamorous%20and%20more%20important%20than%20people%20realize.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20the%20organizer%20in%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findependent-without-close-friends-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efriend%20group%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20I'm%20not%20by%20nature%20an%20organizer.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-husband-and-i-do-laundry-separately-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseparate%20the%20laundry%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20piles%20and%20then%20shove%20the%20clothes%2C%20unfolded%2C%20into%20drawers.%20I'm%20also%20not%20a%20glamorous%2C%20girl%20boss%20who%20makes%20everyone%20wear%20coordinated%20outfits.%20And%20I%20don't%20always%20want%20to%20reach%20out.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20anyone%2C%20I%20can%20feel%20vulnerable%20and%20exposed.%20On%20some%20level%2C%20I'm%20worried%20that%20the%20group%20will%20RSVP%20explaining%20that%20they%20would%20never%20hang%20out%20with%20me%20because%20of%20my%20squinty%20right%20eye%20and%20deep%20love%20of%20puns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20I%20do%20it%20anyway.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229906d888-34cc-4085-8ba0-ac44d2f27f32%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOrganizing%20does%20not%20come%20naturally%20to%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20every%20place%20I've%20ever%20lived%2C%20and%20there%20have%20been%20many%2C%20I've%20been%20the%20one%20who%20makes%20plans%2C%20sends%20out%20that%20invitation%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-i-stopped-chasing-friends-and-finally-found-loyal-friendships-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrings%20friends%20together%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Somehow%2C%20instinctively%2C%20I've%20known%20I%20need%20female%20friends%2C%20and%20to%20have%20them%2C%20someone%20has%20to%20organize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20movies%20and%20television%20shows%2C%20friends%20are%20secondary%20to%20the%20big%20goal%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-fall-in-love-using-science-2017-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinding%20romantic%20love%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20female%20friends%20do%20take%20center%20stage%2C%20like%20in%20the%20Netflix%20show%20%26quot%3BSweet%20Magnolias%26quot%3B%20(about%20three%20absurdly%20well-dressed%20friends%2C%20who%20talk%20sweetly%20over%20gourmet%20snacks)%2C%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Esanitized%2C%20unrealistic%20representations%20are%20another%20problem%2C%20especially%20since%20many%20of%20us%20know%20friendship%20can%20be%20messy.%20It's%20too%20much%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20alternative%20is%20a%20big%20swing%20in%20the%20other%20direction.%20Women%20are%20supposedly%20competition%2C%20and%20the%20media%20delights%20in%20stories%20of%20related%20feuding%20or%20cracks%20in%20high-profile%20friend%20groups%2C%20including%20the%20Spice%20Girls%2C%20Taylor%20Swift's%20%26quot%3Bsquad%26quot%3B%2C%20and%2C%20more%20recently%2C%20the%20Ashley%20Tisdale%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoxic-mom-group-judgment-why-i-left-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emom%20group%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20shows%20like%20%26quot%3BGossip%20Girl%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20cut-throat%20Blair%20Waldorf%2C%20or%20the%20movie%20%26quot%3BMean%20Girls%2C%26quot%3B%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20the%20ultimate%20queen%20bee%2C%20Regina%20George%2C%20the%20organizers%20appear%20to%20be%20the%20rotten%20core%2C%20the%20cancer%20that%20spreads%20via%20text%20or%20a%20three-way%20calling%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ea0c0595-eb27-4735-9719-ef2048ccde99%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFemale%20friendship%20is%20good%20for%20us%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20messaging%20confuses%20the%20facts.%20Female%20friendship%20is%20powerful%20and%2C%20in%20my%20life%2C%20most%20often%20positive.%20Women%20provide%20each%20other%20information%2C%20inspiration%2C%20and%20safety.%20Supported%20by%20friends%2C%20women%20in%20the%20past%20have%20been%20able%20to%20make%20their%20mark%20in%20art%2C%20politics%2C%20and%20everyday%20life.%20Eleanor%20Roosevelt%2C%20for%20one%2C%20became%20more%20self-confident%20and%20a%20better%20leader%20thanks%20to%20friendships%20with%20smart%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apa.org%2Fmonitor%2F2023%2F06%2Fcover-story-science-friendship%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealth%20benefits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too%3A%20scientists%20describe%20friendship%20as%20an%20antidote%20to%20depression%2C%20with%20the%20power%20to%20lower%20blood%20pressure%20and%20overall%20stress.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.womenshealthmag.com%2Frelationships%2Fa68881266%2Ffriendships-slow-aging-study%2F%3Futm_source%3Dgoogle%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dmgu_ga_whm_md_dsa_prog_us_23638537184%26gad_source%3D1%26gad_campaignid%3D23638537184%26gbraid%3D0AAAAACrQpnwmUbjnjGsCupzmDFXGFX2o7%26gclid%3DCj0KCQjw_IXQBhCkARIsADqELbJlU6-ia2XxTlXRzg2qQkrEbo0yHli29V4149f-TULbocge1SZzjawaAj8tEALw_wcB%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOne%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fim-44-and-thought-i-was-done-making-new-friends-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efemale%20friendship%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20also%20slow%20down%20the%20aging%20process%20and%20help%20us%20live%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223369c385-0e96-4e7b-872c-ee94f67d25d7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOrganizing%20a%20friend%20meetup%20doesn't%20need%20to%20be%20complicated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20someone%20doesn't%20reach%20out%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20see%20friends%20and%20experience%20these%20benefits%2C%20especially%20given%20everybody's%20busy%20schedules.%20But%20organizing%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20In%20my%20experience%2C%20it%20also%20doesn't%20require%20matching%20shirts%2C%20power%20plays%2C%20or%20making%20elaborate%20plans.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20go-to%20move%20is%20a%20simple%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskip-coffee-meetings-and-do-this-instead-2015-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoffee%20meet-up%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20whoever%20can%20make%20it.%20It's%20at%20the%20same%20time%20and%20place%20each%20week.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20I%20just%20send%20a%20text%20reminder%20and%20show%20up.%20No%20big-time%20commitment.%20No%20big%20expense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20often%20bring%20work%20or%20a%20book%2C%20just%20in%20case%20there%20are%20last-minute%20conflicts.%20If%20that%20happens%2C%20there's%20no%20bad%20feelings.%20I'm%20happy%20to%20have%20splurged%20on%20a%20sugary%20latte%20while%20getting%20some%20work%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20I've%20tried%20organizing%20dinner%20meet-ups%2C%20but%20there%20were%20always%20too%20many%20conflicts%20%E2%80%94%20both%20in%20scheduling%20and%20dietary%20needs.%20I%20didn't%20enjoy%20the%20negotiations%20before%20or%20after%20the%20bill%20came.%20For%20me%2C%20a%20simpler%20plan%20gets%20the%20job%20done%20without%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20headache%20or%20an%20allergic%20reaction%20to%20shellfish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a5097bc2-84e4-4af8-a492-61bc818bd10f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20learning%20from%20my%20mom's%20example%2C%20but%20doing%20it%20my%20own%20way%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mother%20has%20a%20similar%20standing%20meet-up%20with%20her%20friends%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20are%20retired.%20They%20get%20together%20weekly%20in%20my%20mom's%20garden%2C%20where%20they%20pick%20flowers%2C%20then%20deliver%20bouquets%20to%20a%20memory%20care%20facility%20and%20a%20women's%20shelter.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20my%20mom's%20inspired%20group%20hangout%20is%20more%20than%20my%20group%20can%20manage%20at%20this%20point%2C%20we're%20already%20brainstorming%20about%20the%20next%20phase.%20With%20kids%20who%20will%20soon%20be%20off%20to%20college%2C%20we're%20looking%20forward%20to%20a%20future%20walking%20group%20or%20game%20night.%20No%20one%20seemed%20interested%20in%20my%20idea%20of%20forming%20an%20a%20cappella%20glee%20club.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20we%20all%20come%20to%20coffee%20as%20we%20are.%20I%20try%20to%20shower.%20But%20there's%20no%20obligation.%20And%20there's%20certainly%20no%20evidence%20of%20our%20gatherings%20on%20social%20media.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20might%20have%20a%20higher%20tolerance%20for%20time-consuming%20planning.%20Maybe%20they%20enjoy%20it.%20Of%20course%2C%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20they're%20going%20to%20be%20stylish%20%26quot%3Bmean%20girls%26quot%3B%20either.%20That%20cultural%20trope%20does%20a%20disservice%20to%20women%2C%20whether%20we%20gravitate%20towards%20event%20coordination%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20is%3A%20Anyone%20can%20be%20the%20friend%20group%20organizer%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20have%20to%20fulfill%20stereotypes%20or%20be%20complicated.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20the%20effort%2C%20any%20effort%2C%20is%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-im-the-organizer-in-my-friend-group-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783280641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3aa09a40d09c7636327c7e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-im-the-organizer-in-my-friend-group-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I've%20learned%20that%20strong%20female%20friendships%20don't%20happen%20by%20accident.%20Usually%2C%20someone%20has%20to%20send%20the%20text%20first.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lily%20Hirsch)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20thanks%20Fifa%20for%20spending%20USA%20striker's%20ban%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783280171000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Face%2Fbranded_sport%2F1200%2Fcpsprodpb%2F0bf1%2Flive%2F3ab6d9e0-7898-11f1-9510-1546718f668b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticles%2Fcewqq5q8v41o%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Folarin%20Balogun%20is%20available%20to%20play%20for%20the%20United%20States%20in%20their%20World%20Cup%20last-16%20tie%20against%20Belgium%20after%20his%20one-game%20ban%20is%20suspended%20by%20Fifa.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A96%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticles%2Fcewqq5q8v41o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Venue%2C%20date%2C%20guests%3A%20All%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20Boney%20Kapoor's%20daughter%20Anshula's%20wedding%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1