s%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20has%20released%20its%20latest%20smart%20speaker%2C%20and%20it's%20the%20first%20designed%20with%20the%20brand's%20new%20Gemini%20digital%20assistant%20in%20mind.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D1a013d4c6ef8b545939e5a6179a4b350b1a57ab53a3e87422b6ba59f075fda20%26postID%3D6a46b6db789c4c7dfa6d0899%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fgoogle-home-speaker-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.walmart.com%252Fip%252FGoogle-Nest-Audio-Gen-2-White%252F15932310230%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Home%20Speaker%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20now%20available%20for%20%2499%2C%20and%20it%20comes%20in%20four%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20price%2C%20I%20had%20high%20hopes%20for%20the%20Google%20Home%20Speaker%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20quite%20live%20up%20to%20its%20full%20potential.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20Gemini%20has%20a%20lot%20more%20conversational%20prowess%20than%20the%20brand's%20older%20Google%20Assistant%2C%20plus%20it's%20generally%20more%20knowledgeable%20about%20its%20answers.%20But%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Google%20Home%20Speaker%20isn't%20any%20speedier%20at%20responding%20to%20requests%20than%20my%20Nest%20Hub%20(2nd%20Gen)%2C%20which%20is%20five%20years%20old.%20Plus%2C%20the%20Nest%20Hub%20has%20a%20screen%20for%20added%20functionality%20and%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstore.google.com%2Fproduct%2Fnest_hub_2nd_gen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estill%20available%20for%20%2499%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20those%20quirks%20and%20others%20that%20give%20me%20pause%20in%20fully%20recommending%20the%20Google%20Home%20Speaker.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20speaker's%20volume%20lights%2C%20which%20indicate%20where%20to%20press%2C%20disappear%20when%20not%20in%20use.%20I%20found%20myself%20guessing%20where%20to%20tap%20the%20unit%20more%20than%20I%20would%20have%20liked.%20That%20got%20annoying%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20clear%2C%20the%20Home%20Speaker%20is%20still%20a%20solid%20product%20and%20an%20affordable%20entry%20point%20into%20Google's%20smart%20ecosystem.%20But%20it%20doesn't%20advance%20the%20product%20category%20in%20a%20meaningful%20way.%20Its%20greatest%20sin%20is%20being%20average.%20I've%20tested%20all%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-smart-speakers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20smart%20speakers%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20years%2C%20and%20this%20latest%20one%20from%20Google%20is%20essentially%20a%20HomePod%20Mini%20with%20Gemini%20as%20the%20assistant.%20That's%20not%20necessarily%20a%20bad%20thing%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20very%20exciting%20either.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20thinking%20about%20investing%20in%20Google's%20newest%20smart%20device%2C%20here%20are%20three%20key%20things%20to%20know%20about%20the%20%2499%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D1a013d4c6ef8b545939e5a6179a4b350b1a57ab53a3e87422b6ba59f075fda20%26postID%3D6a46b6db789c4c7dfa6d0899%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fgoogle-home-speaker-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.walmart.com%252Fip%252FGoogle-Nest-Audio-Gen-2-White%252F15932310230%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Home%20Speaker%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d1158263-bf9b-436a-a1bd-1ed336bf3bab%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Gemini%20is%20smart%20but%20not%20a%20magician%5C%22%3EGemini%20is%20smart%20and%20skilled%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20a%20magician%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221694%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Google%20Home%20Speaker%20on%20our%20reviewer's%20dresser%20with%20a%20multi-colored%20LED%20light%20glowing%20at%20the%20base.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a46bad365e65d39ff1c92af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221271%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGemini%20is%20a%20lot%20smarter%20than%20Google%20Assistant%20but%20it%20still%20has%20limitations.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Google%20Home%20Speaker's%20main%20selling%20point%20is%20its%20new%20AI%20assistant%2C%20Gemini%2C%20which%20replaces%20Google%20Assistant.%20When%20comparing%20the%20two%2C%20it's%20almost%20night%20and%20day.%20Gemini%20is%20more%20articulate%20and%20has%20a%20lot%20more%20skills%2C%20like%20being%20able%20to%20understand%20multiple%20commands%20or%20questions%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20having%20access%20to%20Gemini%20on%20a%20smart%20speaker%20isn't%20necessarily%20new.%20Google%20actually%20upgraded%20a%20lot%20of%20its%20older%20Nest%20speakers%20and%20hubs%20to%20support%20Gemini.%20So%2C%20I've%20been%20using%20it%20for%20months%20on%20my%20Nest%20Hub%20prior%20to%20testing%20the%20new%20Home%20Speaker.%20I%20haven't%20noticed%20a%20difference%20in%20Gemini%20performance%20between%20my%20five-year-old%20Nest%20Hub%20and%20this%20new%20device.%20That%20surprised%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20note%20that%20while%20Gemini%20is%20skilled%2C%20it's%20not%20perfect.%20My%20family%20and%20I%20still%20found%20questions%20that%20it%20couldn't%20answer.%20We%20still%20found%20ways%20to%20break%20its%20illusion%20of%20human-level%20intelligence.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20asked%20Gemini%20once%20to%20switch%20the%20music%20it%20was%20playing%2C%20and%20then%20Gemini%20asked%20me%20what%20kind%20of%20music%20I%20wanted%20to%20hear.%20I%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BSurprise%20me.%26quot%3B%20It%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOk.%20Playing%20the%20album%20Surprise%20Me.%26quot%3B%20I%20couldn't%20see%20my%20own%20face%20when%20this%20happened%2C%20but%20I'm%20pretty%20sure%20I%20looked%20like%20the%20deadpan%2C%20straight-faced%20emoji%3A%20%F0%9F%98%91%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20answering%20standard%20queries%2C%20there's%20an%20enhanced%20conversational%20mode%20called%20Gemini%20Live%20that%20you%20can%20toggle%20on%20by%20asking%20the%20Google%20Home%20Speaker%20to%20chat.%20When%20this%20mode%20is%20engaged%2C%20the%20speaker%20stays%20active%20longer%20for%20an%20ongoing%20dialogue%20without%20needing%20to%20keep%20using%20the%20wake%20word.%20This%20functionality%20can%20be%20useful%2C%20but%20only%20sometimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20encountered%20instances%20when%20Gemini%20Live%20mistakenly%20turned%20off%20when%20I%20paused%20for%20too%20long.%20And%20I%20question%20how%20many%20people%20really%20need%20to%20talk%20to%20Gemini%20for%20more%20than%20a%20couple%20of%20minutes%20at%20a%20time.%20Be%20aware%20that%20you%20also%20need%20a%20paid%20subscription%20to%20use%20Gemini%20Live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20AI%20smarts%2C%20the%20Home%20Speaker%20with%20Gemini%20is%20basically%20comparable%20to%20Amazon's%20Alexa%2B%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3Dac4ad4112dba108850cccce9d6e0f90d03f2f01e13c6408aa481a669e0523629%26postID%3D6a46b6db789c4c7dfa6d0899%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fgoogle-home-speaker-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0D6SZKGT4%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEcho%20Dot%20Max%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I've%20used%20each%20on%20and%20off%20for%20normal%20smart%20home%20stuff%20and%20general%20knowledge%2C%20and%20I%20find%20Gemini%20a%20touch%20better%2C%20but%20the%20difference%20is%20mostly%20negligible.%20Going%20through%20enough%20questions%20or%20put%20in%20certain%20circumstances%2C%20you%20could%20probably%20get%20each%20of%20them%20to%20seem%20smarter%20than%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20just%20so%20it's%20clear%2C%20Apple's%20HomePod%20Mini%20with%20Siri%20shouldn't%20even%20be%20in%20the%20conversation%20about%20helpful%20voice%20assistants%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20that%20far%20behind%20Gemini%20and%20Alexa%2B.%20If%20Apple%20puts%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-new-siri-ai-chatbot-app-wwdc-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enew%20Siri%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20HomePod%20device%20in%20the%20future%2C%20then%20it%20will%20be%20worth%20revisiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20point%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D1a013d4c6ef8b545939e5a6179a4b350b1a57ab53a3e87422b6ba59f075fda20%26postID%3D6a46b6db789c4c7dfa6d0899%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fgoogle-home-speaker-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.walmart.com%252Fip%252FGoogle-Nest-Audio-Gen-2-White%252F15932310230%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Home%20Speaker%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20to%20listen%2C%20but%20if%20you%20do%20need%20a%20break%2C%20then%20there's%20a%20microphone%20toggle%20on%20the%20bottom%20to%20mute%20the%20input.%20It%20glows%20orange%20constantly%20to%20let%20you%20know%20it's%20not%20listening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2215408f28-9d83-4188-b199-a3fda9820ad0%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Sound%20quality%20is%20good%20if%20you%20temper%20expectations%5C%22%3EMusic%20sounds%20good%20if%20you%20temper%20your%20expectations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20HomePod%20Mini%2C%20Google%20Home%20Speaker%2C%20and%20Echo%20Dot%20Max%20side-by-side%20on%20a%20dresser.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a46ba55e3bd3a50082bfc6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Apple%20HomePod%20Mini%20(left)%2C%20a%20Google%20Home%20Speaker%20(middle)%2C%20and%20an%20Amazon%20Echo%20Dot%20Max%20(right).%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D1a013d4c6ef8b545939e5a6179a4b350b1a57ab53a3e87422b6ba59f075fda20%26postID%3D6a46b6db789c4c7dfa6d0899%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fgoogle-home-speaker-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.walmart.com%252Fip%252FGoogle-Nest-Audio-Gen-2-White%252F15932310230%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Home%20Speaker%3C%2Fa%3E%20sounds%20good%20overall%20but%20it's%20not%20quite%20at%20the%20level%20of%20similar%20options.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20Gemini's%20voice%20was%20clear%20and%20audible%20in%20various%20situations.%20In%20terms%20of%20music%2C%20the%20speaker%20can%20get%20loud%20enough%20to%20fill%20a%20living%20room.%20At%20a%2050%25%20volume%20or%20less%2C%20songs%20sound%20well-rounded.%20There's%20some%20decent%20bass%20and%20high-end%20present.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20higher%20volumes%2C%20music%20sounds%20more%20strained%20and%20trebly.%20Compared%20to%20bigger%2C%20pricier%20smart%20speakers%2C%20like%20the%20%24189%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D0f257cfc3c71be8591d799359fa8e1a8c1043aaefcc1e216cf162c302895e1f4%26postID%3D6a46b6db789c4c7dfa6d0899%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fgoogle-home-speaker-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0GJ78ZKF6%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESonos%20Era%20100%20SL%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Home%20Speaker%20isn't%20close%20in%20audio%20quality.%20Compared%20to%20the%20Amazon%20Echo%20Dot%20Max%2C%20the%20Google%20Home%20also%20falls%20a%20bit%20short%2C%20with%20less%20bass%20and%20richness.%20To%20be%20clear%2C%20the%20Echo%20Dot%20Max%20isn't%20close%20to%20the%20Sonos%20speaker%20either%2C%20but%20it's%20good%20for%20its%20compact%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Apple's%20HomePod%20Mini%20doesn't%20have%20a%20great%20smart%20assistant%2C%20it%20is%20a%20fine%20speaker.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20Google%20Home%20Speaker%20can%20get%20much%20louder%20than%20the%20HomePod%20Mini.%20At%20modest%20volumes%2C%20the%20Home%20Speaker%20sounds%20a%20little%20better.%20But%20at%20near%20full%20volume%2C%20the%20HomePod%20Mini%20is%20more%20pleasant%20overall.%20It's%20kind%20of%20crazy%20that%20the%20HomePod%20Mini%20debuted%20in%202020%2C%20six%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20it%20still%20holds%20its%20own%20in%20sound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20go%20crazy%20with%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D1a013d4c6ef8b545939e5a6179a4b350b1a57ab53a3e87422b6ba59f075fda20%26postID%3D6a46b6db789c4c7dfa6d0899%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fgoogle-home-speaker-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.walmart.com%252Fip%252FGoogle-Nest-Audio-Gen-2-White%252F15932310230%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Home%20Speakers%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20the%20house%2C%20then%20you%20can%20group%20them%20for%20music%20playback.%20You%20can%20even%20use%20the%20speaker%20in%20a%20home%20theater%20setting%2C%20but%20there%20are%20limitations.%20For%20instance%2C%20I%20would%20have%20loved%20to%20pair%20the%20Home%20Speaker%20with%20Amazon's%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D43da1322d01dacf8f2930292ec3371b6264a9cb337c4d893a251ef08523ca034%26postID%3D6a46b6db789c4c7dfa6d0899%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fgoogle-home-speaker-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAmazon-Ember-Artline-55-inches-with-Fire-TV%252Fdp%252FB0G4XJ6TQ3%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArtline%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20terrible%20built-in%20speakers%2C%20but%20it%20can%20only%20connect%20to%20Google%20TV%20streaming%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Speaker%20doesn't%20have%20Apple's%20AirPlay%2C%20but%20it%20does%20support%20Google%20Cast%2C%20so%20you%20can%20wirelessly%20stream%20from%20apps%20like%20Spotify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2258097c27-b843-485c-bd38-a36f9e2240a2%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22You%20may%20need%20a%20subscription%5C%22%3EYou%20need%20a%20subscription%20for%20advanced%20features%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20a%20Google%20Home%20Speaker%20in%20our%20reviewer's%20home.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a46ba8b65e65d39ff1c92ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECertain%20Gemini%20features%20require%20a%20paid%20subscription%20fee.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20a%20subscription%20needed%20to%20use%20the%20Google%20Home%20Speaker%20with%20Gemini%3F%20No%20%E2%80%94%20but%20also%20yes.%20It's%20complicated.%20Buying%20the%20speaker%20gets%20you%20access%20to%20Gemini's%20basic%20functions%2C%20media%20playback%2C%20parental%20controls%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20broadcast%20messages%20to%20other%20speakers%20in%20the%20home.%20Most%20of%20the%20basics%20that%20you%20would%20assume.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you%20want%20extra%20features%20like%20sound%20detection%2C%20emergency%20calling%2C%20advanced%20AI%20functions%2C%20and%20Gemini%20Live's%20continuous%20conversations%2C%20then%20you%20need%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstore.google.com%2Fproduct%2Fgoogle_home_premium%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Home%20Premium%20subscription%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20subscription%20starts%20at%20%24100%20a%20year%2C%20but%20you%20need%20the%20Advanced%20%24200-per-year%20plan%20to%20unlock%20every%20available%20AI%20feature%2C%20including%20Home%20Brief%2C%20Ask%20Home%20video%20search%2C%20and%20conversational%20automation%20creation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20subscription%20aspect%20quickly%20becomes%20murky.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20Nest%20video%20doorbell%20or%20Nest%20cameras%2C%20then%20you%20might%20already%20have%20a%20Google%20Home%20Premium%20subscription%2C%20which%20this%20Home%20Speaker%20falls%20under.%20You're%20all%20set.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20already%20have%20the%20company's%20cameras%2C%20then%20I%20would%20find%20it%20hard%20to%20justify%20subscribing%20just%20to%20unlock%20this%20speaker's%20extra%20features%2C%20especially%20since%20Gemini's%20continuous%20conversations%20were%20only%20mildly%20useful%20in%20my%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22613bcee9-a864-42b4-bc1d-256c0360b033%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20it%3F%5C%22%3EShould%20you%20buy%20the%20Google%20Home%20Speaker%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Google%20Home%20Speaker%20in%20our%20reviewer's%20hand.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a46bb031bba93485607b01c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Google%20Home%20Speaker%20is%20a%20solid%20device%20but%20it%20doesn't%20offer%20anything%20new.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D1a013d4c6ef8b545939e5a6179a4b350b1a57ab53a3e87422b6ba59f075fda20%26postID%3D6a46b6db789c4c7dfa6d0899%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fgoogle-home-speaker-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.walmart.com%252Fip%252FGoogle-Nest-Audio-Gen-2-White%252F15932310230%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Home%20Speaker%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20fine%20entry%20point%20into%20Google's%20Gemini-powered%20smart%20home%20world.%20For%20%2499%2C%20there's%20nothing%20offensive%20about%20this%20screenless%20speaker.%20Gemini%20is%20fully%20capable%20of%20handling%20most%20requests.%20Newcomers%20will%20probably%20be%20impressed%20by%20its%20conversational%20chops.%20It%20also%20works%20adequately%20for%20music%20and%20audio%20playback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20you%20already%20have%20a%20Google%20speaker%20with%20the%20Gemini%20upgrade%20or%20Alexa%2B%20on%20an%20Echo%2C%20then%20you're%20not%20getting%20much%20that's%20new.%20Google's%20decision%20to%20gate%20some%20niche%2C%20advanced%20AI%20features%20behind%20a%20subscription%20fee%20is%20also%20a%20bummer.%20This%20product%20is%20both%20good%20and%20capable%2C%20but%20also%20boring%20and%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fgoogle-home-speaker-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783266301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a46ba0865e65d39ff1c92a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fgoogle-home-speaker-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20Google%20Home%20Speaker%20with%20Gemini%20is%20smart%20and%20capable%2C%20but%20it%20fails%20to%20stand%20out%20much%20from%20similar%20rivals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Tyler%20Hayes)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20pressured%20countries%20to%20skip%20Khamenei%20funeral%2C%20at%20least%2013%20withdrew%3A%20Reports%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783265938000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132197852%2Cimgsize-180894.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fus-pressured-countries-to-skip-khamenei-funeral-at-least-13-withdrew-or-reduced-participation-reports%2Farticleshow%2F132197649.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F132197649.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20United%20States%20reportedly%20waged%20a%20diplomatic%20campaign%20to%20dissuade%20nations%20from%20attending%20the%20funeral%20of%20Iran's%20former%20Sup