ing%20traffic%20congestion%2C%20officials%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fheavy-rain-causes-waterlogging-traffic-congestion-in-gurugram-11730613%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fheavy-rain-causes-waterlogging-traffic-congestion-in-gurugram-11730613%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fheavy-rain-causes-waterlogging-traffic-congestion-in-gurugram-11730613%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22He's%20making%20%24330%2C000%20secretly%20juggling%202%20jobs.%20He%20says%20it's%20'surreal'%20not%20having%20to%20worry%20about%20money.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22worker%20back%20to%20camera%20at%20desk%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3e91e9a25092c74cc9fba5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Texas%20healthcare%20worker%20is%20earning%20about%20%24330%2C000%20this%20year%20secretly%20juggling%20two%20full-time%20jobs.%3Cp%3EMaskot%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20healthcare%20worker%20is%20making%20%24330%2C000%20secretly%20juggling%20two%20full-time%20jobs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERTO%2C%20layoffs%2C%20and%20employee%20tracking%20have%20forced%20him%20to%20adapt.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20extra%20income%20has%20brought%20financial%20security%2C%20but%20longer%20hours%20have%20also%20fueled%20burnout.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEditor's%20note%3A%20In%20February%202025%2C%20Business%20Insider%20wrote%20about%20a%20medical%20professional%20named%20%26quot%3BDaniel%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20was%20secretly%20juggling%20two%20full-time%20remote%20jobs%20and%20on%20track%20to%20earn%20about%20%24280%2C000.%20(Daniel%20is%20a%20pseudonym%2C%20but%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20his%20identity%20and%20employment.)%20Read%20that%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-two-remote-jobs-same-time-cant-climb-corporate-ladder-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estory%20here%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20In%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20Daniel%20shared%20how%20his%20overemployment%20situation%20has%20evolved.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20Daniel%20last%20year%2C%20secretly%20juggling%20two%20full-time%20remote%20healthcare%20jobs%20was%20relatively%20straightforward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20one%20employer%20has%20required%20him%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbosses-expect-remote-hybrid-workers-in-office-2025-rto-survey-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecome%20into%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20each%20month.%20The%20other%20one%20is%20now%20tracking%20how%20he%20spends%20his%20time.%20To%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20Daniel's%20working%20longer%20than%20ever%20%E2%80%94%20going%20from%20roughly%2040%20to%2050%20hours%20a%20week%20across%20both%20jobs%20to%20as%20many%20as%2060.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20Daniel%20is%20still%20secretly%20juggling%20both%20jobs.%20In%20fact%2C%20he's%20on%20track%20to%20earn%20roughly%20%24330%2C000%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20ever%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20go%20to%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20we%20buy%20whatever%20we%20need%2C%20we%20never%20tap%20into%20credit%20cards%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Daniel%2C%20who's%20in%20his%2040s%20and%20lives%20in%20Texas.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20kind%20of%20surreal%20to%20see%20the%20struggles%20around%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaniel's%20experience%20reflects%20a%20broader%20shift%20in%20the%20overemployment%20movement.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fend-remote-work-could-hurt-overemployed-workers-job-jugglers-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecretly%20juggling%20multiple%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20become%20considerably%20more%20difficult%20amid%20return-to-office%20mandates%2C%20a%20tougher%20job%20market%2C%20layoffs%2C%20and%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femployee-surveillance-how-boss-monitors-your-work-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eemployee-monitoring%20measures%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20changing%20workplace%20norms%20have%20not%20stopped%20workers%20from%20juggling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foveremployment-surviving-return-office-mandates-layoffs-employee-monitoring-tech-workers-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emultiple%20full-time%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Several%20of%20them%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they%20have%20simply%20had%20to%20change%20how%20they%20approach%20the%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20have%20embraced%20AI%20tools%20to%20work%20more%20efficiently%2C%20while%20others%20have%20adapted%20in%20other%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20workers%20like%20Daniel%2C%20the%20financial%20rewards%20remain%20powerful%20enough%20to%20keep%20them%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20is%20speaking%20with%20workers%20who've%20found%20themselves%20at%20a%20corporate%20crossroads%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20due%20to%20a%20layoff%2C%20resignation%2C%20job%20search%2C%20or%20shifting%20workplace%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShare%20your%20story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSechTVqVWQve8iqYssNriCXdtwwdgGRixNNZpmslSKBQqIJ8g%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dheader%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilling%20out%20this%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e0c52d6-0da3-4486-b872-5f4b7b7e5010%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdapting%20to%20overemployment's%20new%20challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20one%20of%20Daniel's%20employers%20began%20requiring%20some%20in-person%20work%2C%20he%20began%20bringing%20his%20other%20job's%20laptop%20to%20the%20office%2C%20carefully%20squeezing%20in%20work%20there%20when%20time%20allowed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20arrangement%20is%20possible%20in%20part%20because%20his%20second%20job%20has%20become%20much%20less%20demanding%20over%20time.%20Additionally%2C%20Daniel%20said%20some%20coworkers%20know%20he%20has%20outside%20work%2C%20which%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foveremployed-millennial-secretly-works-multiple-jobs-catches-job-jugglers-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emade%20him%20less%20concerned%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20being%20discovered.%20In%20his%20experience%2C%20they%20seem%20more%20concerned%20with%20the%20quality%20of%20his%20work%20than%20the%20hours%20he%20spends%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20challenges%20have%20proved%20harder%20to%20solve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20employer%20began%20requiring%20workers%20to%20manually%20track%20how%20they%20spend%20their%20time.%20Daniel%20said%20he's%20delayed%20complying%20for%20as%20long%20as%20possible%2C%20because%20the%20policy%20could%20force%20him%20to%20stretch%20the%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20employer%20also%20conducted%20layoffs%20recently.%20In%20response%2C%20Daniel%20said%20he's%20worked%20to%20maintain%20a%20reputation%20as%20a%20strong%20performer%2C%20taking%20on%20additional%20responsibilities%20and%20positioning%20himself%20for%20a%20potential%20promotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20meant%20working%20considerably%20longer%20hours%20in%20the%20past%20year.%20He%20said%20AI-powered%20medical%20tools%20have%20helped%20offset%20some%20of%20the%20added%20workload%2C%20allowing%20him%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-waiting-ai-productivity-boom-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecomplete%20certain%20tasks%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20quickly%20and%20prevent%20his%20hours%20from%20climbing%20even%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2287cd10f5-5656-4fd5-acf5-a6067b249ade%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20rewards%20of%20job%20juggling%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20tradeoffs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20extra%20income%20from%20job%20juggling%20gives%20Daniel%20plenty%20of%20motivation%20to%20persevere%20through%20the%20challenges%20that%20arise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20he%20purchased%20a%20rental%20property%2C%20hoping%20to%20eventually%20have%20enough%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecession-proof-passive-income-ideas-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epassive%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20reduce%20his%20dependence%20on%20full-time%20work.%20The%20additional%20income%20has%20also%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20cover%20his%20child's%20college%20tuition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20even%20imagine%20going%20back%20to%20just%20a%20single%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20gotten%20used%20to%20the%20income.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20financial%20benefits%20of%20job%20juggling%20have%20been%20substantial%2C%20Daniel%20said%20it's%20come%20with%20tradeoffs.%20His%20desire%20to%20perform%20well%2C%20combined%20with%20a%20heavier%20workload%20and%20the%20demands%20of%20juggling%20two%20jobs%2C%20has%20left%20him%20at%20times%20feeling%20exhausted.%20Though%20he%20remains%20committed%20to%20the%20arrangement%2C%20he%20said%20the%20pace%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20sustain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20like%20every%20day%20I'm%20living%20just%20to%20see%20the%20next%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20I%20need%20a%20vacation%20or%20something%2C%20but%20it's%20doable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ejzinkula%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3