e-for-business-insider-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efreelance%20writer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20editor%20means%20I%20have%20the%20flexibility%20to%20work%20from%20wherever%2C%20whether%20that's%20on%20a%20hospital%20bed%20getting%20induced%2C%20late%20at%20night%20after%20the%20kids%20go%20to%20sleep%2C%20or%20in%20a%20nice%20hotel%20on%20a%20work%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20always%20glamorous%2C%20but%20it%20certainly%20has%20its%20moments%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20joy%20to%20include%20my%20family%20when%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20went%20on%20a%20three-day%20work%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-trip-palm-springs-things-to-do-teens-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrip%20to%20Palm%20Springs%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20about%20a%202%C2%BD-hour%20drive%20from%20our%20home%20in%20San%20Diego%2C%20but%20closer%20to%203%C2%BD%20with%20all%20the%20pit%20stops%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20happy%20that%20the%20hotel%20allowed%20me%20to%20bring%20my%203-month-old%2C%20my%202%C2%BD-year-old%20toddler%2C%20and%20my%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt'd%20be%20my%20first%20time%20bringing%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-mom-kids-hospitalized-on-business-trip-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ekids%20on%20a%20work%20trip%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20our%20first%20overnight%20excursion%20as%20a%20family%20of%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bae86ff8-f268-4561-89d0-52a603e5865c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20wasn't%20sure%20what%20to%20expect%2C%20but%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20spend%20time%20together%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20building%20next%20to%20palm%20trees%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a453f70ec11c5f7e7fa717a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20headed%20to%20Palm%20Springs%20in%20a%20car%20packed%20with%20essentials.%3Cp%3ECarmen%20Varner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20car%20was%20packed%20to%20the%20brim%20with%20diapers%2C%20clothes%2C%20carriers%2C%20and%20anything%20else%20we%20could%20think%20of%20for%20a%20multi-night%20stay%20away%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20just%20gotten%20back%20from%20my%20first-ever%20work%20press%20trip%20away%20from%20the%20kids%20the%20day%20before%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20had%20returned%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburned-out-late-20s-quit-job-travel-career-break-travelries-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ework%20trip%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20before%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20experiences%20on%20hold%20with%20my%20first%20child%20and%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20do%20the%20same%20with%20my%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20feeling%20overbooked%2C%20I%20said%20yes%20to%20both%20trips%20and%20was%20glad%20to%20take%20my%20family%20along%20for%20the%20second%20one%3B%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20away%20from%20them%20again%2C%20at%20least%20not%20in%20such%20a%20rapid%20succession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20with%20my%20husband%20and%20me%20both%20traveling%2C%20we%20just%20want%20to%20spend%20a%20couple%20of%20nights%20together%20as%20a%20family.%20I%20knew%20I'd%20be%20busy%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20intense%20the%20trip%20would%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2201372354-5bf8-4ae7-8f95-b7644b3e9023%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENavigating%20work%20commitments%20and%20family%20was%20challenging%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222939%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Toddler%20holding%20railings%20at%20a%20hotel%2C%20looking%20at%20body%20of%20water%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a453f70ec11c5f7e7fa7179%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20toddler%20enjoyed%20exploring%20the%20hotel%20grounds.%3Cp%3ECarmen%20Varner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20day%20one%2C%20I%20was%20shuttled%20around%20with%20a%20couple%20of%20other%20journalists%20for%20a%20three-course%20lunch%20and%20a%20dessert%20tasting.%20During%20breaks%20and%20at%20night%2C%20I%20rushed%20back%20to%20the%20hotel%20to%20help%20my%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recall%20walking%20into%20the%20hotel%20the%20first%20night%20to%20him%20baby-wearing%20the%203-month-old%20in%20a%20carrier%20while%20patting%20my%20toddler's%20back%3B%20both%20were%20successfully%20asleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20night%2C%20we%20all%20slept%20soundly%20through%20the%20whole%20night%2C%20unbothered.%20The%20next%20day%20was%20not%20nearly%20as%20streamlined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20scheduled%20events%2C%20I%20returned%20to%20the%20hotel%20for%20a%20quick%20break%20to%20nurse%20and%20was%20out%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20my%20husband%20was%20behind%20on%20work%2C%20since%20he%20couldn't%20do%20virtually%20anything%20with%20the%20two%20young%20kids%2C%20other%20than%20entertain%20them%20and%20explore%20the%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22arancini%20balls%20in%20pool%20of%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a453f702680585ce91a318b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222419%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20brought%20a%20lot%20of%20food%20back%20to%20the%20hotel%20room%20for%20us%20to%20try.%3Cp%3ECarmen%20Varner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20night%2C%20I%20nursed%20the%20baby%20and%20patted%20my%20toddler's%20back%20at%20the%20same%20time%20so%20my%20husband%20could%20work.%20I%20kind%20of%20felt%20like%20a%20superhero%20there%20for%20a%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20they%20were%20finally%20sleeping%20soundly%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20hung%20out%20in%20the%20bathroom%20since%20the%20hotel%20room%20was%20otherwise%20one%20big%20open%20area%2C%20and%20we%20didn't%20want%20to%20wake%20them%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20whispered%20next%20to%20the%20shower%2C%20eating%20the%20cold%20mashed%20potatoes%20I'd%20brought%20back%20from%20an%20event.%20After%20that%2C%20we%20both%20attempted%20to%20catch%20up%20on%20work%20on%20our%20laptops%20and%20ultimately%20went%20to%20sleep%20exhausted%20%E2%80%94%20but%20our%20night%20didn't%20end%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20baby%20woke%20up%20more%20times%20than%20we%20could%20count%2C%20and%20the%20toddler%20roused%20from%20all%20the%20hubbub%2C%20too.%20We%20were%20drained%20and%20exhausted%2C%20and%20all%20I%20could%20think%20of%20was%20that%20I%20had%20to%20be%20up%20early%20for%20a%20tour%20of%20a%20date%20farm%20at%208%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22860b5ab7-644b-4e25-8505-870d6b97ca64%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDespite%20all%20the%20hubbub%2C%20I'd%20happily%20do%20this%20again%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20smiling%20while%20holding%20baby%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a453f702680585ce91a318a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUltimately%2C%20it%20was%20nice%20to%20share%20a%20new%20experience%20with%20my%20husband%20and%20kids.%3Cp%3ECarmen%20Varner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20fun%20going%20out%20for%20a%20few%20hours%20at%20a%20time%20and%20being%20an%20adult%20without%20having%20to%20monitor%20two%20kids%2C%20but%20I%20came%20back%20to%20reality%20every%20break%20and%20evening%20at%20the%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGranted%2C%20my%20husband%20did%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20work%20while%20I%20was%20out%20and%20about%2C%20but%20it'll%20remain%20a%20family%20memory%20and%20a%20trip%20we%20otherwise%20would've%20never%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20the%20disarray%2C%20I%20still%20got%20to%20share%20parts%20of%20the%20experience%20with%20my%20children%3A%20bringing%20back%20restaurant%20dishes%20to%20try%20together%2C%20watching%20my%20toddler%20take%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhotels-with-great-views-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%