2C%20maybe%20you%20can%20stretch%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2258788727-4984-4f52-8f4a-db0bef8b98b9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20still%20do%20things%20we%20can%20do%20at%20home%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20we%20all%20saw%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-way-to-see-tokyo-go-kart-tour-review-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ego-cart%20place%3C%2Fa%3E%20we%20just%20passed%20on%20the%20highway.%20But%20we%20are%20in%20Barcelona.%20And%20why%20on%20earth%20would%20we%20waste%20a%20precious%20afternoon%20in%20Catalonia%20doing%20what%20we%20can%20do%2020%20minutes%20from%20home%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20somehow%2C%20it%20will%20be%20an%20adventure%2C%20different%20than%20the%20place%20back%20home%20in%20interesting%20and%20unexpected%20ways%2C%20and%20you%20will%20all%20actually%20have%20fun.%20Do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221b107a6a-47ff-4486-ab22-a68a9afdfd0e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20like%20to%20explore%20cities%20in%20different%20ways%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbudapest-places-to-skip-and-what-to-see%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecity%20tour%20of%20Budapest%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20do%20it%20riding%20a%20three-wheeled%20Segway.%20My%20kids%20love%20to%20look%20for%20the%20weird%20way%20to%20sightsee%20now%2C%20and%20they%20actually%20learn%20a%20ton%20about%20our%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222049%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Family%20riding%20bikes%20with%20sidecars%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a343a6ef4bed3c6152cbc22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20family%20likes%20to%20explore%20new%20cities%20in%20different%20ways.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Marrakesh%2C%20we%20toured%20the%20city%20from%20the%20vantage%20of%20Soviet-era%20motorcycle%20sidecars.