%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Family%20at%20a%20cooking%20class%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a39ce0cd175c90a6a6fac0a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221404%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20suggests%20taking%20a%20cooking%20class%20when%20traveling.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20both%20love%20to%20cook%20(we%20do%20too)%20so%20this%20is%20a%20destination%20%26quot%3Bsouvenir%26quot%3B%20that%20we%20cherish%20and%20refer%20back%20to%20again%20and%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d857c217-1bf9-404c-b0b5-4193f3f880f5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EScreen%20time%20is%20flexible%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20only%20they%20would%20put%20the%20phone%20down%2C%20they%20could%20appreciate%20the%20incredible%2C%20once-in-a-lifetime%20view.%20But%20spending%20every%20minute%20traveling%20(and%20maybe%20sharing%20a%20hotel%20room)%20with%20your%20parents%20can%20be%20tough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20are%20spending%20more%20time%20than%20you'd%20like%20on%20their%20device%2C%20but%20still%20otherwise%20engaged%2C%20I%20let%20it%20slide.%20Offer%20to%20help%20by%20being%20the%20photographer%20and%20shoot%20them%20in%204%2C567%2C354%20poses%20for%20their%20one%20IG%20%26quot%3Bpost%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20trip.%20There.%20Now%20you've%20made%20it%20a%20family%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227e173c48-51e1-4c9c-8725-6e6df46da2c9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDivide%20and%20conquer%20to%20do%20what%20everyone%20loves%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20loves%20golf%20%E2%80%94%20I%20couldn't%20care%20less.%20So%20we%20build%20in%20some%20divide-and-conquer%20time%20when%20we%20each%20do%20what%20we%20love.%20(And%20hey%2C%20they're%20teens%20now%2C%20so%20they%20don't%20need%20me%20every%20minute!)%20I%20walked%20the%20Canyon%20Road%20galleries%20in%20Sedona%2C%20having%20the%20best%20morning%20of%20my%20life%2C%20while%20my%20son%20took%20his%20dad%20to%20play%20nine%20hole