20460%2C000%20(over%20%2410%2C000)%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20number%20of%20days%20at%20the%20front%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-troops-walk-30-km-supply-lines-disrupted-mykhailo-fedorov-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMykhailo%20Fedorov%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ukraine's%20defense%20minister%2C%20described%20them%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bhighest%20salaries%20in%20the%20world%20for%20infantry%2C%26quot%3B%20calling%20these%20front-line%20roles%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20difficult%20and%20risky%20job%26quot%3B%20right%20now.%20He%20said%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20fill%2030-50%25%20of%20these%20positions%20with%20foreigners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20jobs%20can%20be%20some%20of%20the%20deadliest.%20Front-line%20positions%20are%20often%20described%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drone-kill-zone-is-getting-bigger-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekill%20zones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20threat%20of%20drones%20making%20it%20hard%20not%20only%20to%20survive%20but%20even%20to%20get%20there%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20Pay%20can%20be%20a%20strong%20motivation%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20now%20that%20a%20large%20number%20of%20foreigners%20are%20coming%20to%20Ukraine%20to%20fight%2C%20because%20today's%20salary%20is%20already%20attracting%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Fedorov%20said%20last%20month.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we're%20talking%20about%20an%20increase%2C%20then%20this%20will%20attract%20even%20more%20foreigners%2C%20and%20then%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20strengthen%20our%20front%20line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Leary%20said%20the%20higher%20pay%20and%20longer%20contracts%20could%20help%20if%20they%20push%20foreign%20fighters%20to%20stay%20for%20a%20year%20or%20more.%20The%20problem%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20that%20many%20of%20them%20have%20historically%20treated%20six%20months%20as%20the%20endpoint%2C%20leaving%20Ukraine%20with%20little%20return%