3b62535f6ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20with%20her%2064-year-old%20friend%20at%20a%20Manhattan%20coffee%20shop.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jacqueline%20LeKachman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EQuitting%20my%20full-time%20job%20to%20go%20to%20grad%20school%20sent%20me%20into%20major%20money-saving%20mode.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20Gen%20X%20and%20Boomer%20friends%20had%20larger%20budgets%2C%20and%20I%20worried%20when%20they%20routinely%20paid%20for%20me.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20one%20of%20my%20friends%20said%20something%20wise%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20slowly%20release%20my%20anxiety.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20steady%20job%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmamdani-controversial-free-bus-and-childcare-services-affordability-new-yorkers-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%20public%20high%20school%20teacher%20to%20start%20a%20full-time%20graduate%20program%20in%20Manhattan.%20I%20worried%20about%20the%20choice%20not%20only%20because%20I%20loved%20my%20work%20with%20the%20kids%2C%20but%20also%20because%20I%20had%20traded%20a%20consistent%20paycheck%20and%20affordable%20health%20insurance%20for%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20tuition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20teaching%2C%20I%20prepared%20for%20the%20cost%20by%20scrimping%20to%20save%20every%20cent%20I%20could.%20But%20my%20account%20balance%20still%20wouldn't%20fully%20cover%20two%20years%20of%20school%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadult-sons-moved-back-in-expenses-increase-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20expenses%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20my%20savings%20journey%2C%20I%20learned%20a%20lot%20of%20lessons%2C%20especially%20from%20my%20older%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223f223ae2-aa09-4941-9720-f6152fbc6f79%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20jumped%20into%20major%20money-saving%20mode%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20I%20redoubled%20my%20frugal%20efforts.%20I%20made%20a%20rule%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20eat%20out%20or%20order%20takeout%20unless%20it%20was%20someone's%20birthday.%20I%20asked%20to%20meet%20people%20in%20parks%20rather%20than%20restaurants%20and%20suggested%20%245%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhappy-hour-spots-nyc-wall-street-bars-nightlife-stone-street-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehappy-hour%20spots%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20meticulously%20crafted%20list%20on%20my%20phone.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20rare%20occasions%20when%20I%20dined%20out%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20the%20prices%20before%20deciding%20what%20to%20order%20and%20pored%20over%20the%20bill%20with%20a%20calculator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20worked.%20While%20it%20was%20still%20difficult%20to%20watch%20my%20savings%20dwindle%20%E2%80%94%20buoyed%20occasionally%20by%20small%20deposits%20from%20part-time%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%20I%20kept%20my%20costs%20(relatively)%20low%20for%20a%2020-something%20in%20the%20city.%20Most%20friends%20understood%20my%20restrictions%20or%20were%20in%20similar%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275040958-2518-47a6-a3c7-ef84abd45fcd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20worried%20when%20my%20older%20friends%20routinely%20paid%20for%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20approach%20didn't%20work%20as%20well%20with%20my%20five%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F30-year-old-woman-prefers-hanging-out-with-elderly-friends-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eolder%20friends%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20my%20intergenerational%20writer's%20group.%20We'd%20been%20meeting%20weekly%20on%20Zoom%20for%20several%20years%20when%20we%20started%20visiting%20each%20other%20in%20our%20home%20states%20across%20the%20country.%20As%20women%20in%20their%2040s%20and%2060s%20in%20dual-income%20households%20with%20established%20careers%2C%20they%20understandably%20gravitated%20toward%20nicer%20places%20where%20the%20cheapest%20cocktail%20cost%20%2420.%20My%20dive%20bars%20with%20weirdly%20stained%20walls%20weren't%20going%20to%20cut%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20visited%20two%20of%20these%20friends%20in%20Chicago%2C%20I%20anticipated%20that%20we'd%20go%20to%20swanky%20spots%20and%20saved%20up%20for%20weeks%2C%20cutting%20out%20anything%20nonessential%20from%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-vs-costco-grocery-shopping-price-comparison-better-review-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrocery%20list%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20chocolate-covered%20pretzels%2C%20bananas%2C%20frozen%20fried%20rice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20I%20offered%20to%20chip%20in%20for%20our%20multi-course%20dinners%20or%20luxury%20spa%20day%2C%20they%20brushed%20me%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20grateful%20for%20their%20generosity%2C%20yet%20overcome%20with%20guilt.%20They%20had%20contributed%20so%20much%20to%20our%20time%20together.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20a%20freeloader%2C%20the%20friend%20who%20couldn't%20hold%20up%20her%20end%20of%20the%20deal.%20How%20could%20I%20pay%20them%20back%20and%20show%20my%20appreciation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20trip%2C%20my%20friend%20Andrea%2C%2046%2C%20and%20I%20ate%20lunch%20in%20a%20diner%20in%20the%20Gold%20Coast.%20I%20made%20one%20last%20offer%20to%20Zelle%20her.%20In%20response%2C%20she%20said%20something%20that%20stuck%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20in%20my%2020s%2C%20people%20helped%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me%20with%20an%20easy%20smile.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%2040%2C%20just%20pay%20it%20forward%20by%20buying%20a%20younger%20woman%20dinner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2235b7ccfb-01f4-444f-8fd9-e5b3b5303248%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHer%20wisdom%20helped%20me%20slowly%20release%20my%20anxiety%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20mulled%20over%20her%20words%20on%20the%20plane%20home.%20I%20was%20surprised%20that%20her%20view%20of%20the%20situation%20differed%20so%20much%20from%20mine%2C%20and%20relieved%20she%20didn't%20see%20me%20as%20taking%20advantage%20of%20her.%20Yet%20it%20was%20still%20hard%20to%20fully%20let%20go%20of%20the%20weight%20in%20my%20chest%20%E2%80%94%20the%20feeling%20of%20being%20indebted%20to%20someone's%20kindness%2C%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-simple-hack-that-completely-changed-how-i-give-gifts-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccepting%20a%20gift%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20knowing%20you%20can't%20reciprocate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonths%20later%2C%20my%2064-year-old%20friend%20from%20my%20writer's%20group%20visited%20from%20Florida.%20We%20went%20out%20for%20coffee%2C%20and%20I%20thought%20to%20myself%2C%20%3Cem%3EOkay%2C%20now%20this%20I%20can%20afford%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20when%20I%20offered%20to%20cover%20or%20at%20least%20split%20it%2C%20she%20waved%20me%20off%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20treat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20of%20Andrea's%20words%20and%20told%20myself%2C%20%3Cem%3EShe's%20being%20nice.%20Don't%20worry%20about%20it%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThank%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20said%2C%20and%20meant%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20while%20later%2C%20when%20another%20friend%20visited%20from%20Washington%2C%20she%20paid%20most%20of%20our%20checks%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-exclusive-restaurants-regularmaxxing-central-perk-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebars%20and%20restaurants%3C%2Fa%3E%20we%20visited.%20Though%20I%20felt%20a%20twinge%20of%20the%20usual%20panic%20at%20first%2C%20by%20our%20second%20day%20together%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20let%20it%20go.%20As%20we%20wandered%20through%20the%20Upper%20West%20Side%2C%20the%20tightness%20in%20my%20chest%20lifted%2C%20leaving%20only%20gratitude%20that%20she%20was%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fa311550-edad-458c-bce8-b8668ad3bc72%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20do%20plan%20on%20paying%20it%20forward%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAndrea%20was%20right%2C%20I%20realized.%20Helping%20each%20other%20was%20what%20friends%20did%2C%20and%20they%20clearly%20weren't%20bothered%20by%20it.%20Sure%2C%20I%20wasn't%20paying%20for%20lavish%20things%20or%20hosting%20people%2C%20but%20I%20shouldn't%20let%20my%20own%20hangups%20affect%20our%20time%20together%2C%20which%20always%20produces%20some%20of%20my%20favorite%20memories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20I'll%20be%20able%20to%20do%20what%20they've%20done%20for%20me%20for%20another%20woman%2C%20who%20can%20then%20help%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20worrying%2C%20now%20I%20let%20my%20friends'%20kindness%20bring%20us%20together%20and%20smile%2C%20knowing%20that%20every%20time%20I%20pay%20for%20a%2020-something%20woman%20in%20the%20future%2C%20I'll%20think%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrad-student-on-budget-struggled-accept-help-gen-x-friends-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783252021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a440810a25092c74cca1942%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrad-student-on-budget-struggled-accept-help-gen-x-friends-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Quitting%20my%20full-time%20job%20for%20grad%20school%20sent%20me%20into%20saving%20mode.%20My%20older%20friends%20started%20paying%20for%20me%2C%20which%20made%20me%20uncomfortable%20at%20first.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jacqueline%20LeKachman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CM%20Yadav%2C%20Scindia%20lay%20foundation%20for%20Adani%20defence%20manufacturing%20unit%20in%20MP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A178325120400