y%20since%20styling%20can%20cost%20anywhere%20from%20a%20few%20hundred%20to%20a%20few%20thousand%20dollars%20per%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Waliji%20initially%20charged%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20for%20services%20like%20closet%20cleanouts%2C%20following%20industry%20standards%2C%20she%20has%20since%20lowered%20her%20prices%20to%20reach%20more%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20now%20charges%20%242%2C000%20for%20in-person%20capsule%20wardrobe%20consultations%2C%20%24450%20per%20hour%20for%20private%20style%20consulting%2C%20and%20%24250%20for%20virtual%20closet%20cleanouts%2C%20where%20she%20connects%20with%20clients%20over%20Zoom%20and%20helps%20them%20decide%20whether%20to%20keep%20or%20remove%20each%20piece%20of%20their%20wardrobe.%20Clients%20may%20pay%20extra%20to%20purchase%20new%20pieces%20that%20help%20stylists%20fill%20gaps%20in%20clients'%20wardrobes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223715%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zahra%20Waliji%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3c29f7e218c3b62535c48a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222477%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EVictor%20Llorente%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20tried%20to%20master%20the%20skill%20of%20buying%20inexpensive%20clothes%20and%20making%20them%20look%20very%20high-end%2C%26quot%3B%20Waliji%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'll%20practice%20on%20myself%20and%20style%20a%20look%20from%20head%20to%20toe%20for%20%2475%2C%20so%20I%20know%20it's%20doable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20celebrity%20styling%20and%20personal%20styling%20merge%2C%20though%2C%20is%20in%20the%20art%20of%20tailoring.%20It's%20not%20always%20the%20clothes%20themselves%20that%20make%20A-listers%20stand%20out.%20It's%20the%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%5BClients%5D%20can%20buy%20a%20pair%20of%20pants%20for%20%2425%2C%20invest%20another%20%2430%20to%20get%20them%20hemmed%20or%20to%20get%20the%20waist%20taken%20in%2C%20and%20then%20the%20entire%20look%20is%20ele