0customers%20have%20standout%20pieces%20to%20add%20to%20their%20closets%2C%20and%20stylists%20have%20new%20social-media%20content%20they%20can%20use%20to%20promote%20their%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latter%20has%20proven%20especially%20beneficial%20for%20stylists%20who%20take%20their%20services%20online%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20niche.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40stylingwithkenzie%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKenzie%20Welch%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20them.%20She%20styles%20everyday%20people%20with%20modern%20pieces%20and%20films%20their%20makeovers%20as%20part%20of%20an%20ongoing%20TikTok%20series.%20Her%20videos%20have%20gained%20her%201.3%20million%20followers%2C%20more%20than%2028.2%20million%20likes%2C%20and%20a%20plethora%20of%20new%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVideos%20like%20Welch's%20often%20inspire%20people%20who%20never%20before%20considered%20working%20with%20stylists.%20Through%20social%20media%2C%20they%20uncover%20that%20styling%20is%20an%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDQ-cNhUjQSR%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDQ-cNhUjQSR%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C