%3Cp%3EConsider%20vacations.%20Buying%20new%20pieces%2C%20turning%20them%20into%20cute%20outfits%2C%20and%20making%20sure%20you%20don't%20forget%20anything%20when%20you%20pack%20requires%20time%20and%20energy%20that%20many%20people%20don't%20have.%20Stylists%20can%20ease%20that%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223715%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zahra%20Waliji%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3c2a74360acd489560a816%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222477%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EVictor%20Llorente%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20have%20clients%20say%3A%20I%20have%20a%2010-day%20vacation%2C%20and%20I%20need%20you%20to%20style%20me%20for%20daytime%20and%20nighttime%20looks.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20think%20about%20it.%20I%20want%20you%20to%20help%20me%20pack%20so%20when%20I%20go%20there%2C%20I%20know%20exactly%20what%20I'm%20wearing%2C%26quot%3B%20Waliji%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'll%20do%20that%2C%20and%20I'll%20take%20pictures%20%5Bof%20each%20outfit%5D%20so%20they%20have%20a%20guide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ultimate%20luxury%20that%20results%20from%20personal%20styling%2C%20though%2C%20is%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20struggled%20with%20body%20image%20issues%20and%20confidence%20my%20entire%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Waliji%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20she%20understands%20the%20emotional%20side%20of%20styling.%20%26quot%3BWorking%20with%20women%20and%20men%20to%20make%20them%20feel%20powerful%2C%20strong%2C%20and%20empowered%20every%20day%20creates%20a%20kind%20of%20happiness%20that%20nothing%20else%20can%20bring.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20client%20of%20Waliji's%20works%20as%20a%20teacher%20in%20New%20York.%20Her%20personal%20uniform%20consists%20of%20a%20simple%20blazer%20and%20trousers%20every%20day%20%E2%80%94%20no%20accessories%2C%20skirts%2C%20or%20fancy%20hairstyles%20included.%20When%20Waliji%20styled%20her%20for%20a%20party%2C%20though%2C%20she%20realized%20she%20could%20actually%20color%20outside%20the%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20was%20talking%20about%20my%20outfit%20at%20my%20party%2C%20and%20I%20was%20turning%20a%20lot%20of%20heads%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20teacher%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20who%20I%20see%20every%20day%20at%20work%20got%20to%20see%20me%20in%20a%20new%20light.%20It%20was%20a%20big%20deal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENaysayers%20might%20argue%20that%20there's%20no%20need%20to%20spend%20on%20personal%20styling%20when%20you%20can%20get%20fashion%20advice%20for%20free%20from%20a%20friend%2C%20a%20store%20salesperson%2C%20TikTok%2C%20and%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStylists%20and%20their%20clients%20disagree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223434%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zahra%20Waliji%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3c2aa0a25092c74cc9e69c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222290%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EVictor%20Llorente%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20working%20with%20a%20client%2C%20and%20I%20picked%20a%20Zimmerman%20dress%20for%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20Waliji%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20she%20put%20it%20on%2C%20she%20said%2C%20'This%20is%20it.%20I%20want%20every%20dress%20to%20make%20me%20feel%20this%20way.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20made%20an%20effort%20to%20understand%20what%20makes%20her%20feel%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20really%20get%20that%20from%20TikTok.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20you%20never%20know.%20If%20you%20can't%20afford%20a%20stylist%20but%20you%20meet%20one%20like%20Waliji%2C%20you%20might%20get%20lucky.%20Styling%2C%20she%20believes%2C%20should%20be%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20money%20to%20get%20in%20the%20way%20of%20making%20you%20feel%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20bad%20businesswoman.%20I've%20worked%20with%20people%20for%20no%20cost.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ET