-land-rovers-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elast%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20him%20think%20hard%20about%20how%20he%20wanted%20to%20spend%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20life%2C%20and%20what%20meaning%20it%20would%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20couldn't%20be%20about%20one%20more%20weekend%20when%20I%20said%20goodbye%20to%20my%20family%20on%20a%20Saturday%20afternoon%20so%20I%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburned-out-constant-travel-took-relaxing-vacation-worth-it-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etravel%20for%20more%20than%20twenty%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20arrive%20in%20China%20for%20a%20meeting%20first%20thing%20on%20Monday%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fretirement-planning%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretiring%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Blankfein%20has%20been%20free%20to%20spend%20his%20days%20taking%20courses%20in%20physics%20and%20linguistics%2C%20perusing%20military%20histories%20and%20biographies%2C%20and%20taking%20on%20other%20intellectual%20pursuits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20able%20to%20pursue%20my%20curiosity%20freely%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20has%20felt%20like%20a%20luxury%20and%20a%20gift%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlankfein%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-lloyd-blankfein-stock-market-sectors-tech-energy-finance-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrades%20his%20personal%20account%20daily%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20%26quot%3Bit's%20fun%20for%20me%20to%20make%20bets%20on%20the%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20offers%20advice%20and%20punditry%2C%20supports%20nonprofits%2C%20and%20spends%20more%20time%20with%20his%20family%20as%20well%20as%20exercising%20and%20traveling%20for%20leisure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20recalled%20in%20his%20memoir%20that%20when%20he%20made%20partner%20at%20Goldman%2C%20he%20was%20advised%20that%20his%20go