-paramount_n_699ec72de4b0dce804cd0415%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20intense%20bidding%20war%20for%20the%20studio%20behind%20Batman%20and%20Harry%20Potter%20has%20reached%20a%20fever%20pitch.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fwarner-bros-reopens-door-to-paramount_n_699ec72de4b0dce804cd0415%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-huffpost-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fwarner-bros-reopens-door-to-paramount_n_699ec72de4b0dce804cd0415%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fwarner-bros-reopens-door-to-paramount_n_699ec72de4b0dce804cd0415%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22She%20Lost%20Both%20Parents%20as%20a%20Teen%20but%2022-YO%20Rupam%20Kept%20Her%20Promise%20%26amp%3B%20Cleared%20JPSC%20in%201st%20Attempt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20quiet%20evening%20at%20the%20hospital%20in%20Ranchi%20when%20two%20sisters%20clutched%20their%20mother%E2%80%99s%20frail%20hands.%20Sixteen-year-old%20Rupam%20Sonali%20held%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20face%20gently%2C%20her%20eyes%20brimming%20with%20tears%20she%20refused%20to%20shed.%20Moments%20later%2C%20their%20world%20changed%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Rupam%20and%20her%20elder%20sister%20Rupali%2C%20life%20would%20never%20be%20the%20same%20again.%20Their%20father%20had%20passed%20when%20Rupam%20was%20just%2011%2C%20and%20now%2C%20within%20a%20week%20of%20being%20diagnosed%20with%20blood%20cancer%2C%20their%20mother%20too%20was%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRelatives%2C%20instead%20of%20offering%20support%2C%20distanced%20themselves.%20We%20were%20only%20two%20daughters%2C%20and%20society%20was%20cruel%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rupam%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20told%20us%20we%20had%20no%20future%2C%20that%20we%20were%20helpless%20without%20parents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quo