20girl%20with%20little%20interest%20beyond%20studies.%20I%20now%20speak%20freely%20and%20motivate%20other%20girls%20in%20my%20class%20to%20step%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20her%20biggest%20dream%2C%20her%20eyes%20light%20up%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20represent%20India.%20I%20want%20my%20jersey%20to%20say%20India%20on%20the%20back.%E2%80%9D%20Alongside%2C%20she%20hopes%20to%20one%20day%20serve%20as%20an%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%20officer%20or%20in%20the%20Navy.%20But%20her%20first%20love%20will%20always%20be%20football.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20what%20if%20the%20OSCAR%20Foundation%20had%20never%20existed%3F%20Without%20OSCAR%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20be%20nothing%2C%20just%20a%20girl%20doing%20studies%2C%20living%20a%20boring%20life.%20OSCAR%20gave%20me%20hope%2C%20a%20dream%2C%20and%20the%20courage%20to%20chase%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20Ashok%E2%80%99s%20journey%20began%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Yamini%20and%20thousands%20like%20her%2C%20the%20turning%20point%20was%20Ashok%20Rathod%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20pick%20up%20a%20football%20in%20his%20neighbourhood%20nearly%20two%20decades%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%2C%20Ashok%20had%20watched%20friends%20slip%20into%20addiction%20or%20drop%20out%20of%20school%2C%20while%20he%20himself%20struggled%20in%20college.%20Coming%20from%20a%20Hindi-medium%20background%2C%20English%20lectures%20left%20him%20alienated%2C%20and%20without%20guidance%2C%20he%20dropped%20out%20in%20his%20second%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-3-1757076466.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yamini%20Nikam%2C%20once%20a%20reluctant%20participant%2C%20found%20confidence%20and%20a%20second%20home%20in%20football%20through%20the%20foundation.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-3-1757076466.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-3-1757076466-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-3-1757076466-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-3-1757076466-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-3-1757076466-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-497011%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EYamini%2C%20once%20a%20reluctant%20participant%2C%20found%20confidence%20and%20a%20second%20home%20in%20football%20through%20the%20foundation.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20seemed%20like%20failure%20became%20the%20beginning%20of%20his%20life%E2%80%99s%20purpose.%20With%20no%20grand%20plan%2C%20he%20began%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331811%2Fraees-ahmed-coach-football-sport-talent-in-bicharpur-mini-brazil-madhya-pradesh-inspiring-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egathering%20kids%20to%20play%20football%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20were%20on%20the%20field%20with%20me%2C%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20on%20the%20streets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%2018%20children%2C%20the%20numbers%20grew%20to%20hundreds.%20By%202009%2C%20150%20kids%20were%20playing%20regularly.%20That%20same%20year%2C%20Ashok%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20were%20recognised%20nationally%20%E2%80%94%20he%20received%20the%20CNN-IBN%20Real%20Hero%20Award%20from%20Nita%20Ambani%20and%20Aamir%20Khan%2C%20along%20with%20Rs%203.45%20lakh%20in%20prize%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-